                                    <span>_______________________________________</span><br/>
                                    <p style="font-size:18px;">Employer</p><br/>
                                    <b><t style="font-size:20px;text-align:center;" class="text-uppercase" t-esc="str(o.get_approvers_name(signatory_id.id)).upper()"/></b>
